- `org.apache.http`
- `com.squareup.retrofit2`

Since all the imports in this code are from:
1. The `android.*` namespace (Android SDK - standard platform library)
2. The same package (`com.udinic.accounts_authenticator_example.authentication`)

There are **no external/third-party dependencies** in this code.
